						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">Chōḻa, Madiraikoṇḍa Parakēśarivarman, Year 38 = 945 A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>Seems to record a decision taken by the assembly of Tiruttaṇiyal towards some provisions for performing the <hi rend="italic">śrīkāiryam</hi> of Subrahmaṇya temple on the top of the hill. Refers that they met in a hall <hi rend="italic">(ambalam)</hi> constructed by one Sāttūruḍaiyāṉ Sāttaṉ of Maḻanāḍu.</p>						

						</summary>
